Package: HaploGeno
Title: Haplotype-Based Genomic Prediction
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: person("Zachary", "Aldiss", email = "zaldiss@illinois.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Zachary Aldiss [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Zachary Aldiss <zaldiss@illinois.edu>
Description: Implements a high-performance framework for haplotype-based genomic prediction and QTL discovery. 
    Leverages file-backed matrices via 'bigstatsr' to handle large-scale genomic datasets efficiently. 
    Key features include LD-based haplotype block construction, kernel ridge regression (KRR) for genomic prediction, 
    and local genomic estimated breeding value (GEBV) analysis for identifying significant genomic regions.
